Sacred Almanac: Traces of Greed (2015) PC [FINAL]
============================================

- ENG

============================================
Description:                               =
============================================

The mysterious disappearance of chief engineer Jonathan Finch interrupts the construction of a trunk railway. The head of the company sends film footage with records of an accident to his friend, ex-army officer Richard Stone. Richard's is the first to notice the stone monument, and its origin becomes a perplexing riddle for him to solve. Having agreed to participate in the investigation, Richard doesn't suspect yet that he takes the dangerous path of a defender of an ancient civilization.

============================================
FEATURES:                                  =
============================================

- 32 animated and picturesque game scenes
- 21 challenging logic-based minigames
- Interactive game map prevents you from getting lost
- Exciting cut-scenes and fascinating dialogue

